{"tid":1771153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[mini game] 講感受 送你一個詞語！","createTime":"2019-12-05T15:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T06:17:14.000Z","uid":127064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc8fc746dfaed560cb64060a42b480eb50d7254","tid":1771153,"uid":127064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:47:52.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇興趣參與以下既活動<br />\n<br />\n用一句句子去summarize你既感受 關於乜都得 (I.e. relationship, family, hk etc.)<br />\n<br />\n而我會送一個英文詞語比你 但唔會講原因<br />\n<br />\n你認識咗個詞語之後大約用5 minutes 去諗下依個詞語點解 點樣connect到去你既感受 <br />\n<br />\n如果唔太認識個詞語 上網搵英文definition 再諗諗<br />\n<br />\n諗完之後 你想既可以分享返 唔想既就睇下人地分享<br />\n<br />\n每一個英文詞語都係正面既 目的係希望係依個時期鼓勵支持下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f3e40f5fbf1440c9d5d1140d10978465830122","tid":1771153,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:50:39.000Z","msg":"I am happy."},{"pid":"e6f2f78bd8a799a814f1738342e886ab99076080","tid":1771153,"uid":127064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1f3e40f5fbf1440c9d5d1140d10978465830122","tid":1771153,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:50:39.000Z","msg":"I am happy."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;Meaning&rsquo;"},{"pid":"d84bc20b701cb588474ab0eda90492d6463f15c0","tid":1771153,"uid":333993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"lonely lonely Christmas"},{"pid":"c451dc4805df26f64371d358709408a9407dce17","tid":1771153,"uid":127064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d84bc20b701cb588474ab0eda90492d6463f15c0","tid":1771153,"uid":333993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"lonely lonely Christmas"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;Hope&rsquo;"},{"pid":"3f9ec7a3d4535138796cb8a97f9c4ac55f02595b","tid":1771153,"uid":127064,"like":0,"dislike":0